        ".       In the autumn of 1928, with October still under fire in many Soviet quarters, Eisenstein left the Soviet Union for a tour of Europe, accompanied by his perennial film collaborator ": null
    },
    {
        "Grigori Aleksandrov": "Grigori Aleksandrov"
