    },
    {
        ", on behalf of ": null
    },
    {
        "Paramount Pictures": "Paramount Pictures"
    },
    {
        ", offered Eisenstein the opportunity to make a film in the United States.  He accepted a short-term contract for $100,000 and arrived in Hollywood in May 1930, along with Aleksandrov and Tisse.     Eisenstein proposed a biography of munitions tycoon ": null
    },
    {
        "Basil Zaharoff": "Basil Zaharoff"
    },
    {
