        "  An American Tragedy .  This excited Eisenstein, who had read and liked the work, and had met Dreiser at one time in Moscow. Eisenstein completed a script by the start of October 1930,  but Paramount disliked it completely and, additionally, found themselves intimidated by Major ": null
    },
    {
