        "Bolshoi Theatre": "Bolshoi Theatre"
    },
    {
        ". After the outbreak of war with Germany in 1941, Alexander Nevsky was re-released with a wide distribution and earned international success. With the war approaching Moscow, Eisenstein was one of many filmmakers evacuated to ": null
